<h3 class='col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 center home_section_header '>Why?</h3>

<div class='row '>
  <div class='what_container section_block col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1'>
    <div class="section_body">
      <p>
        Yasub lets you easily translate any internet video and share it with people in a way where original video content owners are credited properly. This is done via softsubs, where subtitles you create are simply overlayed to the original video. No more reprinting, re-encoding, and reuploading to a separate channel. 
      </p>
      <br>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<h3 class='col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 center home_section_header '>Recently Created</h3>

<div class='row'>
  <!-- <h3 class='col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 center home_section_header'>Videos</h3> -->
  <div class='latest_videos videos videos_container section_block col-md-10 col-md-offset-2 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1'>
    <div class="home_try section_body">
      <% @repos.each_slice(5) do |repos| %>
        <%= render partial: "repositories/list", locals: {repos: repos, repo_width: "col-md-2"}  %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class='header-section col-xs-12'></div>
